data.description: Imagine having free roaming chickens and goats and your own hobby farm! Looking for room to ride quads or horses? The setting on over 5 acres is perfect for nature lover's of all kinds. Over 2400 sq ft one owner custom built ranch! Great floor plan with open feel and great views of nature all around! 3 large bedrooms. 2 full baths. Owner's suite bath has both walk in shower and nice soaker tub. Main floor laundry room. Large kitchen with lots of storage. Full basement that has endless possibilities. Massive 4+ car attached garage and 32'x40' metal pole building ready for the woodworker or car enthusiast with 200 amp electric. Ontario School District.
